  <span id="freeText14575385898734764192" style="display:none">Not sure why this one didn't resonate more with me. Perhaps because I'd seen the film and some of the plot was, well, spoiled? Perhaps because I had trouble keeping the characters apart? I dunno. At any rate, it's a fine story, and well written. Not sure I'd rank it as in my favorite war fiction, but I'm happy I read it.</span>
