  <span id="freeText10452019349943562368" style="display:none">I recently found out that William Wharton was especially appreciated in Poland which I found intriguing. I am an avid reader of his and enjoyed this little book as well. Although I don't seem to gravitate towards war-related subjects, this one kept me captivated from the beginning to the end. The ending was truly intense too.</span>
