<li class='cover' id='bookCover_109378'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/109378.The_Orientalist"><img alt="The Orientalist: Solving the Mystery of a Strange and Dangerous Life" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1367256909l/109378._SX98_.jpg" />
